summary: Dwemer themed player home with all the bells and whistles.
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds a Dwemer themed player home along the river east of Riften. I plan to expand on the house later on, maybe add a quest once I learn more about the CK.

House includes:
Bed
Chests
Re-spawning ingredient barrels
Re-spawning Alchemy satchels
Bookshelves
Armor Mannequins
Display cases
Weapon racks
Weapon plaques
Shield Plaques
Cooking spit
Enchanter
Alchemy lab
Smelter
Workbench
Grinding wheel
Tanning rack
Anvil
Talos shrine

Version history:
v1.0 
-Initial release

v1.1 
-Replaced re-spawning chests in The blacksmith room with non re-spawning chests, added chest next to the enchanter

v1.2 
-added the tanning rack (not sure how I managed to miss this before)
-fixed the gap in the bedroom
-added a couple dagger racks
-added a porch and some seating out front
-added non re-spawning barrels next to the cooking spit

If anyone out there knows what steps I need to take to make the house companion friendly I\'d really appreciate the help. 

This mod is presented as is, with no warranty. It has been tested, however you should back up your game before
installing and using.

This mod was made from scratch by me, you may not upload it to another site without my permission.
You are free to modify it as you please on your own system.
If you upload work that uses my mod please give me credit.

If you find a bug please report it to me on the Nexus.

Happy gaming! If you like the house please endorse! I put a lot of work into making it.
author: wclancey
